lead_paragraph: For months, Jeb Bush has been dogged by questions about his family's presidential legacy, and the formal announcement of his White House candidacy on Monday will do little to quell them.

headline.main: The Best Thing for Jeb Bush Could Be Hillary Clinton
headline.print_headline: The Best Thing for Jeb Bush Could Be Hillary Clinton
